name: The Simpsons Did It - Mr. Burns - VARIANT
description:
Regularly Scheduled Programs, The Simpsons Did It, is a glitched out tribute to the golden years of The Simpsons. Seasons 2-11 not only took place during my childhood but featured some of the best writing, storylines, and laugh out loud jokes of any TV show ever. 
Collect Bart, Lisa, Homer, and Marge and get Mr. Burns FREE!
Utilizes Please Stand By - I Got Something To Say 049
THIS WAS ONLY AVAILABLE TO THOSE WHO BOUGHT "THE FIRST 100 PIECE" or THROUGH A TWITTER RAFFLE.
